title: Chantilly Lace (1993) Ally Sheedy Jill Eikenberry et al
description:
After all the serious stuff I have been putting up, here is a feel-good movie devoted to the power of female friendship. Apparently the obviously talented cast was told to just go in front of the camera and improvise, the results are quite impressive. Let the girls cast their spell on you...

I am surprised no-one has put this up yet. In segmented mpg format, plays on VLC, but you might have difficulty burning it.
